We will have Fried_Chicken , Baked_Potatoes and Ice_Cream for all the children !
We ' ll also have fun games and events for the children , and lots of really cool prizes !
There are a total of 155 children of all ages ranging from infants ( age 0 ) to teenagers age 16 as well as about 20 elderly age over 60 who have no living relatives to care for them .
I hope to gather a target of 45 volunteers to help with the event .
Please note that you should confirm your attendence before clicking on " Going/Attending " as we will save your seat on the bus from Ho_Chi_Minh_City to the Orphanage in Dong_Nai .
